ekhon ar ekta sidebar e setting er moddhe option add koro seta holo SEO setting. 

ekhane ekta image uploader thakbe ei image ta hobe website er default og image jeta use kora hobe jokhon kono page share kora hobe social media te jodi oi page er specific og image na thake.
tarpor thakbe meta description ar meta keywords er field gula.
er por thakbe meta keywords ekhane select2 use koro jate multiple keywords add kora jai.
social title  ar social description er field thakbe.

ei gulo properly implement korba jekhane jhekha lagbe sei gulo te.